{"tid":2508812,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"內地客急沽土瓜灣利．港灣18海景戶　料損手逾230萬","createTime":"2021-04-29T04:44:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T05:37:43.000Z","uid":24730,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"43d327d26421ed23d54a5b0186f122734eaeefc3","tid":2508812,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T04:44:01.000Z","msg":"內地客急沽土瓜灣利．港灣18海景戶　料損手逾230萬<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n地產樓市<br />\n<br />\n撰文：李彤<br />\n2021-04-29 09:30<br />\n最後更新日期：2021-04-29 09:30<br />\n<br />\n市場消息指，土瓜灣利．港灣18一伙高層B單位，實用面積534平方呎，三房套房間隔，望啟德郵輪碼頭全海景，議價後以約1,052萬元易手，呎價19,700元。<br />\n<br />\n據知，原業主為內地客，於2016年底斥約1,285.4萬元一手買入上址，成交價創當時項目的標準戶新高，惟業主持貨僅五年，據知因急於套現，現易手帳面蝕233.4萬元，連使費等估計實際損手近300萬元，此為屋苑首宗蝕讓個案。<br />\n<br />\n利．港灣18位於土瓜灣浙江街18號，由有利集團發展，屬單幢盤，於2014年開售。"},{"pid":"25287901b148ba54817ca1860633810c0700e94b","tid":2508812,"uid":228955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T05:01:55.000Z","msg":"有錢就移民攞綜援攞資源繼續留喺度"},{"pid":"734eaa3d2905098e67ffab8adfbfe4ab87cb5aaa","tid":2508812,"uid":373119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T05:24:21.000Z","msg":"呢啲畜生業主做壞規矩<br />\n一齊企硬個價一定有人買"},{"pid":"7e899c20d905ae57ab0560d8dadaea3ba8c9975c","tid":2508812,"uid":214502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T05:25:08.000Z","msg":"樓價gogogo<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"276ee0ed7aee5d6ba18fa0f2422b8279ce94f7df","tid":2508812,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T05:25:55.000Z","msg":"開咗關會唔更多蝕讓盤<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd265eaadcdb080300b94c6c6cee16fa0d8d3904","tid":2508812,"uid":156542,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T05:36:12.000Z","msg":"土瓜灣 溢價咁高 <br />\n預咗死硬"},{"pid":"4af40a5b0a96a32033dd2634c31a6b5ebd5b7cf8","tid":2508812,"uid":187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T05:36:54.000Z","msg":"唔講